I fixed it on this file below.
superset/assets/src/visualizations/deckgl/utils.jsx

function getBuckets
>> before
  buckets[range] = {
     color: colorScaler({ [fd.metric.label || fd.metric]: mid }),
     enabled: true,
   };

>> after
  const metricLabel = fd.metric ? fd.metric.label || fd.metric : null;
   buckets[range] = {
     color: colorScaler({ [metricLabel || fd.metric]: mid }),
     enabled: true,
   };

I was running into errors on a fresh install. `boto3` / `botocore` should really be an optional dependency as basic installation shouldn't require it.

Added a note in `UPDATING.md` noting that people may need a new way to install this dep.

